934
00:52:00,793 --> 00:52:02,554
Pak!

935
00:52:02,554 --> 00:52:04,524
Panggil ambulans!

936
00:52:04,524 --> 00:52:07,393
Bisakah seseorang memanggil ambulans?

937
00:52:07,393 --> 00:52:09,493
Bertahanlah!

938
00:52:09,493 --> 00:52:11,263
Sampai ambulans datang,

939
