dan aku dimarahi, aku akan membunuhmu.

982
00:54:01,674 --> 00:54:02,888
Baik, Pak.

983
00:54:04,284 --> 00:54:05,419
Jadi,

984
00:54:06,313 --> 00:54:09,254
bagaimana dengan kasus gangguan bisnis?

985
00:54:09,254 --> 00:54:10,329
Apa?

986
00:54:10,754 --> 00:54:12,154
Aku menunggu

987
00:54:12,154 --> 00:54:15,329
Industri Jeongsu mengirimkan beberapa berkas.

988
00:54:15,623 --> 00:54:17,798
Berkas? Omong kosong.

989
00:54:18,563 --> 00:54:20,568
Kasusnya sudah ditutup.

990
00:54:21,034 --> 00:54:24,238
