999
00:54:53,293 --> 00:54:54,609
Ini Cho Min Ho.

1000
00:54:57,864 --> 00:54:59,008
Ya.

1001
00:55:04,944 --> 00:55:06,079
Aku mengerti.

1002
00:55:06,643 --> 00:55:07,789
Ya.

1003
00:55:17,123 --> 00:55:18,729
"Untuk persetujuan"

1004
00:55:19,824 --> 00:55:20,968
Tulis ulang.

1005
00:55:22,424 --> 00:55:23,493
Apa?

1006
00:55:23,493 --> 00:55:24,723
"Untuk persetujuan"

1007
00:55:24,723 --> 00:55:25,868
Ini juga.

1008
00:55:26,623 --> 00:55:27,709
Apa?

1009
00:55:30,194 --> 00:55:31,838
Park Jae Sik.

1010
00:55:32,534 --> 00:55:33,979
Dia meninggal.

1011
